reviews.text: Excellent food we loved every dishes we tried here!

I wish I can give this restaurant a 2.8 rating. The food was ok, but definitely not at the Dragon King level quality which we expected, having frequented their Causeway Bay and Hopewell branches. Service wasn’t bad, but they were understaffed before 11am when we seated. One positive was the reasonable price, although that is like due to the early hours.

I would not recommend it unless you’re simply desperate for dim sum. There are better restaurants in this building.
Great food exceeded our expectations.
